Properties
The Tutte polynomial factors into connected components. If 
  
    
      
        G
      
    
    {\displaystyle G}
   is the union of disjoint graphs 
  
    
      
        H
      
    
    {\displaystyle H}
   and 
  
    
      
        
          H
          ′
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle H'}
