        y
        ,
        x
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle T_{G}(x,y)=T_{G^{*}}(y,x)}
  Especially, the chromatic polynomial of a planar graph is the flow polynomial of its dual. Tutte refers to such functions as V-functions.

