            +
            m
          
        
        =
        O
        
          (
          
            1.6180
            
              n
              +
              m
            
          
          )
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle t(n+m)=\left({\frac {1+{\sqrt {5}}}{2}}\right)^{n+m}=O\left(1.6180^{n+m}\right).}
  The analysis can be improved to within a polynomial factor of the number 
  
    
      
        τ
        (
